sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant KubeAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as OGX Operator<br/>(Reconciler)
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine<br/>(embedded)
    participant OGXPod as OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as Remote Provider<br/>(vLLM/OpenAI/Azure/etc.)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB<br/>(PGVector/Milvus/Qdrant)

    Note over User,VectorDB: Flow 1: OGXServer Reconciliation

    User->>KubeAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    KubeAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ogx-io-v1beta1-ogxserver<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS serving cert
    Webhook-->>KubeAPI: Allowed (validated distribution,<br/>provider IDs, references)
    KubeAPI->>Operator: Watch event: OGXServer created/updated<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token

    Operator->>Operator: Generate config.yaml from CR spec<br/>(provider configuration)
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests from base templates<br/>(namespace, name-prefix, field mutation,<br/>network policy transform, autoscaling)
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered K8s resources

    Operator->>KubeAPI: Create/Update ConfigMap (config.yaml)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>(with config hash annotation)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Create/Update Service (ClusterIP)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Create/Update NetworkPolicy<br/>(auto-injects kube-dns egress)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Create/Update PVC, HPA, PDB,<br/>ServiceAccount, RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Operator,OGXPod: Status Health Check
    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Provider info response
    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Version info response
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Update OGXServer status<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over User,VectorDB: Flow 2: OGX Server Inference Request

    User->>OGXPod: POST /v1/inference<br/>HTTP(S)/8321<br/>Application-level auth
    OGXPod->>Provider: Forward to remote provider<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>API key / IAM credentials
    Provider-->>OGXPod: Inference result
    OGXPod->>VectorDB: Vector I/O query<br/>TCP (configurable port)<br/>Password / Token auth
    VectorDB-->>OGXPod: Vector results
    OGXPod-->>User: Inference response

    Note over User,VectorDB: Flow 3: Legacy Adoption Migration

    User->>KubeAPI: Create OGXServer CR with adoption annotations<br/>(ogx.io/adopt-storage, ogx.io/adopt-networking)
    KubeAPI->>Operator: Watch event: OGXServer with adoption annotations
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Scale legacy LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Deployment to 0 replicas
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Wait for legacy pods to terminate
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Adopt PVCs: remove old ownerRef,<br/>relabel for new OGXServer
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Adopt Services: update selectors<br/>to route to new pods
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Adopt Ingresses: transfer ownership
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Record audit timestamp annotations
    Operator->>KubeAPI: Create new Deployment with<br/>adopted PVC mounts
